     FAB#PWBV CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                        RRN1  KSFILE SFL01
     F                                        RRN2  KSFILE SFL02
     F                                              KINFDS @INFDS
     FAB#PL19CIF  E           K        DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAL#PL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#WPBV UF  E           K        DISK                      A    UC
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     E                    CMD     1   4 78
     E                    MSG     1   5 78
     E                    CLS     1   2 70
     E*
     E                    SDT         3  8
     E                    @@A         3  5 0
     E*
     E                    #DT         3  8
     E                    #DS         3 14
